# Local RAG Chat

A fully local RAG pipeline with a Gradio UI, using LangChain, Qdrant in-memory vector store, and Ollama.

## Installation
```bash
pip install --index-url [https://test.pypi.org/simple/](https://test.pypi.org/simple/) local-rag-chat
